<!-- DEVELOPMENT -->

<div class="row">
  <div id="development">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <center>
          <h4 id="devRowHeader">We use the best tools and technologies around.</h4>
        </center>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div id="devRow1">

          <!-- NODE.JS -->
          <div id="nodejs" class="six columns rowItem">
            <div class="itemLogo">
              <img src="../images/node.png" class="itemLogoImg">
            </div>
            <p><strong>We use <a href="http://nodejs.org/" target="_blank">Node.js</a> to build blisteringly fast application backends that are capable of delivering data in real-time.</strong>
              Nothing will give your customers a more impressive experience than seeing your app living and breathing as they use it.
              From real-time Twitter feeds to chat apps, if you bring the idea, we can use Node.js to make it a reality.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- MONGODB -->
          <div id="mongodb" class="six columns rowItem">
            <div class="itemLogo">
              <img src="../images/mongo.png" class="itemLogoImg">
            </div>
            <p><strong>Gone are the days when managing a database had to be difficult.</strong> <a href="http://mongodb.org/" target="_blank">MongoDB</a> gives you the flexibility to change the way you store and retrieve data with minimal impact,
              while maintaining the same level of security that you expect.
              Combined with its incredible speed, Mongo makes housing data an absolute breeze.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div id="devRow2">

          <!-- SOA -->
          <div id="soa" class="six columns rowItem">
            <div class="itemLogo">
              <img src="../images/soa.png" class="itemLogoImg">
            </div>
            <p><strong>Why worry about building your app multiple times for different platforms?</strong> By using service-oriented architecture, we ensure that any device in the world that can talk to the internet is able talk to your app.
            From smartphones to tablets to digital billboards, we make sure that your product is consumable by any modern device on the web.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- SCALABLE -->
          <div id="scalable" class="six columns rowItem">
            <div class="itemLogo">
              <img src="../images/aws.png" class="itemLogoImg">
            </div>
            <p><strong>Spend your time growing your product, not worrying about downtime.</strong> We use the most reliable cloud hosting platforms in the industry to ensure your product can handle incredible amounts of traffic.
              With platforms like <a href="http://aws.amazon.com/" target="_blank">AWS</a> and <a href="http://heroku.com/" target="_blank">Heroku</a>, you can disrupt your industry without disrupting your uptime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
